<p begin="01:22:37.870" end="01:22:40.380" style="s2">be a real partner because they don’t know<br />who the hell you are.</p>
<p begin="01:22:40.380" end="01:22:41.810" style="s2">And then you’re weak because there’s only<br />one of you.</p>
<p begin="01:22:41.810" end="01:22:42.810" style="s2">Yeah?</p>
