<p begin="01:24:12.880" end="01:24:17.320" style="s2">Well they’re not a slice, they’re a whole<br />damn thing, this thing that grows across time.</p>
<p begin="01:24:17.320" end="01:24:21.190" style="s2">Okay, who else has something to say that’s<br />interesting?</p>
